│ 16348 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed till the     │
│ 16349 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions and further  │
│ 16350 /// analysis/transformations.                                                     │
│ 16351 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle instructions  │
│ 16352 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                                   │
│ 16353 /// For example, given the code                                                   │
│ 16354 /// \code                                                                         │
│ 16355 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                               │
